Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:29.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yoshii.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:33.30,Main,,0,0,0,,I know I don't have\Na nice figure after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:37.68,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not really true. You're slim\Nand the right places are protruding, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:41.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. My bust is slim\Nand my belly is protruding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:43.85,Main,,0,0,0,,No one said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:48.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:51.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.86,0:10:53.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you wearing your top?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Because this is a men's swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,A girl shouldn't wear a men's swimsuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,You're mistaken!\NListen to me! I'm saying, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:12.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Minami, did my\Nbrother make a blunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.43,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Minami?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:21.51,Main,,0,0,0,,It's okay. I know I'll never\Nbe able to beat that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Akira, excuse me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.06,0:11:28.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.23,0:11:30.94,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Please excuse me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:38.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Beaches are cruel, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:40.74,Main,,0,0,0,,It's God who's cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:44.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I took so long, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Hideyoshi?\NYou seem to be down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Please don't ask me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beaches in summer{\i0}\N{\i1}are cruel in many ways.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot Test!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.48,0:12:10.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, it's more to your right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.73,0:12:12.77,Main,,0,0,0,,That's not true.\NIt's actually more to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:15.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii, keep going straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.24,0:12:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's telling the truth?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:24.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Aki, it's 32 degrees\Nleft at a distance of 4.7m.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It's actually at the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone's giving me{\i0}\N{\i1}different instructions. What do I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What about Yuuji?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, what do you\Nthink of this swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Nothing, really.\NI saw it before, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.97,Main,,0,0,0,,That's because you aren't seeing it\Ncarefully. You should see it up closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:44.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't get so close!\NAll sorts of things are touching me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:47.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It's... right... there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.81,0:12:51.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.61,Main,,0,0,0,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.61,0:12:54.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Tsk! I missed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:13:00.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yuuji.\NI thought it was a watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:03.16,Main,,0,0,0,,It looked as if you\Ndashed with no hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.37,0:13:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you saying, Hideyoshi?\NThat's a terrible misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,He's right, Hideyoshi. All Akihisa was\Ndoing was looking for the watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:19.55,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?\NLet go of the bat, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:22.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You tried just a little earlier and failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The first round is over. It's the\Nsecond round now and I go first, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:29.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just fair to do it in the\Nopposite order in the second round.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:33.19,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm, we don't really want to smash\Nthe watermelon, so why don't we stop
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:35.19,Main,,0,0,0,,the watermelon cracking game now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:38.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! We're definitely\Nnot gonna crack the watermelon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.32,0:13:41.24,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you guys going to crack?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't even swum yet.\NWhy am I so exhausted?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.75,0:13:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,You asked for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:55.04,Main,,0,0,0,,We bought lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:56.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry that it took us a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Was it crowded?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:59.51,Main,,0,0,0,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:02.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, we got hit on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:04.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I really don't like stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Me, neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:08.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. That must've been a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:11.10,Main,,0,0,0,,You can just laugh it off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.10,0:14:12.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, both of you.\NThat kind of attitude isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, you don't get how\Nwomen's minds work, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. You should\Nbe more worried, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:27.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! About wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.20,0:14:29.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Argh! My bones...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:34.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I wish Akihisa got jealous\Nover us, too, even just a little bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:37.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, why don't we\Nmake him worry a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.88,0:14:42.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Guys like that are everywhere.\NIt's such a pain, right, Mizuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.34,0:14:45.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're always bothering us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.51,0:14:50.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Do you two often get hit on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:52.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes! We get hit on all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:54.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! We get hit on everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.73,0:14:58.06,Main,,0,0,0,,But, you guys seemed\Nlike you weren't used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:58.98,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:03.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true! Since it happens\Nall the time, we were just disgusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.32,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,though you may not get it since\Nyou're dull and a stranger to relationships!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.33,Main,,0,0,0,,How rude! If we're talking\Nhitting on girls, I, too, can easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:14.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--Easily what?\N--Easily what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:19.84,Main,,0,0,0,,To start with, there's no\Nway you can hit on girls, Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.84,0:15:23.05,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right! Hitting on\Ngirls doesn't suit you, Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.05,0:15:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't think it'll work, either!\NYou shouldn't put up a front!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,You don't get a woman's heart either,\NYuuji. That's why you're unpopular.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:33.73,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare you say\Nsomething like th-- Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone has his or her\Nstrengths and weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You're not suited for relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.69,0:15:47.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Damn! I can't take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was unfairly scolded.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,How can they say we're unpopular?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:57.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! If I get serious, I can\Nhit on as many girls as I... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:58.54,Main,,0,0,0,,"Argh"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:01.50,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Akihisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:04.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I saw an unbelievable sight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:08.43,Main,,0,0,0,,...is being hit on...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:09.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:12.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini is being hit on by girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:16.56,Main,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous. I keep telling\Nyou to cut it with the nonsense talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:19.40,Main,,0,0,0,,You're a genius at\Ntaking pictures, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:21.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is nothing special.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're being shy,\Naren't you? How cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:30.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening...\NWhy is Muttsulini...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:33.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:35.25,Main,,0,0,0,,This is just hypothetically speaking...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:39.50,Main,,0,0,0,,but could you and I be the only\Nones among us who're unpopular?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!\NThat can't be right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:48.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! There's no way\Nthat's the case, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:54.01,Main,,0,0,0,,At a glance, Muttsulini\Nlooks completely harmless, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:55.89,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just that he's a different\Ntype from us, that's all, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.89,0:16:58.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so it'd be premature\Nto think that we're unpopular!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.73,0:17:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, right?! How dare they\Nsay that there's no way I can hit on girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll show them what I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.23,0:17:07.03,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the spirit, Akihisa! Let's show\Nwhat we can do when we get serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:11.24,Main,,0,0,0,,"Thinking back on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,something must've been\Nreally wrong with us at that time."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,In any case, how do we\Ngo about hitting on girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.58,Main,,0,0,0,,The quickest route would\Nbe to imitate a successful guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:24.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's follow Muttsulini's example.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.55,Main,,0,0,0,,We target those who're\Ntrying to take pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:31.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the first person will start\Nby creating an opportunity, saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:32.80,Main,,0,0,0,,"I can take your picture if you like."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:33.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:37.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, if the second person\Ngets a conversation going,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:39.60,Main,,0,0,0,,the rest will go without a hitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:42.02,Main,,0,0,0,,So how do we get a conversation going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.02,0:17:44.81,Main,,0,0,0,,That's something the second\Nperson has to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:47.90,Main,,0,0,0,,So if the whole thing fails,\Nit'd be the second person's fault, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:54.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You jerk, Akihisa! Why are\Nyou running like a maniac?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,You too, Yuuji!\NWhat's with that crazy running?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You take your time and come later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:02.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You {\i0}should do that!\NI'll create an opportunity, so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:05.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't trust you! Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Not a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.55,0:18:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting!\NWell then, I'll take your picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.34,0:18:15.39,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Gasping, gasping... Gasping, gasping..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:19.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Miss... you're pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:24.23,Main,,0,0,0,,If you like, I can take...\Na picture of you in a swimsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I never thought that\Nthey'd call the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.49,0:18:38.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Using pictures to create an\Nopportunity might be tough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:43.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Unlike Muttsulini,\Nwe're not good at taking pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:46.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay then, let's change the approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.38,Main,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.38,0:18:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,How about we praise the target's\Nlooks to thaw the ice and get close?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.05,0:18:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, people like being praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.30,Main,,0,0,0,,But how do we praise them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.30,0:18:59.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Use figurative expressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:02.89,Main,,0,0,0,,like telling them they resemble\Nsome showbiz person or athlete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:07.06,Main,,0,0,0,,If you compare them to someone\Nand get the conversation going...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.06,0:19:08.73,Main,,0,0,0,,...it'll be a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm... you're pretty, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.45,Main,,0,0,0,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:21.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you've got an outstanding figure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.33,0:19:24.50,Main,,0,0,0,,I think so, too! It's really nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you guys are good at flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.67,0:19:28.63,Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's not flattery!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:31.42,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right! We really think that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.42,0:19:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You've really got a\Nnice figure. You're just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:36.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:39.85,Main,,0,0,0,,You're just like one of the\Nnude models in dirty magazines!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.35,0:19:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What a right hook she had...\NShe could be a world champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:53.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet that lady is a future champion\Nbecause I even feel it in my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:57.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where have you two been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Gulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.20,0:19:59.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Your faces are swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:00.45,Main,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,N-Nothing, really, right, Yuuji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.95,0:20:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah! We just fell,\Nthat's all. Right, Akihisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.41,0:20:08.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji! Let's go back to\Nthe swimming competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:11.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm not gonna lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,We were finally close to succeeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,But since you said\Nsomething uncalled for...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:20.22,Main,,0,0,0,,That's because you said stupid stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?! Are you\Ntrying to pin this all on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:24.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You jerk... Are you picking a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:29.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's not. Fighting won't get us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.81,0:20:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You know, I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:36.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you think things go bad\Nbecause we're not really serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:42.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I mean, since they're not our types,\Nwe're unconsciously holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:45.99,Main,,0,0,0,,True... If we can't get serious,\Nthen what can we do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.96,Main,,0,0,0,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,That's an uncool excuse, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.76,0:21:07.85,Main,,0,0,0,,All right, then! Why don't\Nwe try one last time with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.85,0:21:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:14.07,Main,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,A-Actually... we got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.24,0:21:24.62,Main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, we're looking for the\Nswimming beach, do you know where it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:28.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiot! {\i1}This {\i0}is the swimming beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,You said we got lost,\Nso without thinking, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:21.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.05,0:22:28.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Her hair color... changed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:33.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:35.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.73,0:22:36.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.44,0:22:38.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:42.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.74,0:22:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Muttsulini?! Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:47.66,Main,,0,0,0,,They were giving off a vibe that\NI was going to be killed if I refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.66,0:22:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I-Is it possible that you guys\Nknew we were hitting on girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:52.91,Main,,0,0,0,,They said just the right arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.91,0:22:56.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Just the right arm, huh?\NIt sounds painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.38,0:22:58.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:23:01.71,Main,,0,0,0,,They said they'd spare just the\Nright arm and break everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:09.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa, please stay where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.06,0:23:12.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to give you a full-course\Npunishment today. Be prepared, Aki!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.81,0:23:16.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Your sister feels sad...\Nabout losing her little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.90,0:23:18.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Run, Akihisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:20.69,Main,,0,0,0,,These three are serious about hurtin--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:25.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Akihisa... We had a lot of fun together.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:29.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:35.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.71,0:23:37.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:37.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Sit in a formal way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:40.63,Main,,0,0,0,,What? But we're in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.63,0:23:41.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sit in a formal way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.76,0:23:44.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, we're in the ocean so...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.21,0:23:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you going to make me say it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:51.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Sit in a formal way...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.47,0:23:53.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Question 2.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.56,0:23:57.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Aside from water, what is the{\i0}\N{\i1}primary component of seawater?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.27,0:23:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tears of regrets and penitence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What happened?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:01.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.73,0:24:03.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Me, Yukata, and Festivities!"{\i0}
